# Quant Fox

**Quant Fox** is a next-generation AI-powered trading simulator designed for modern investors. Built for accessibility and edge, it gives users:

- 💰 A simulated $1M trading account
- 📈 Options trade simulation in real time
- 🤖 AI chatbot using GPT-4, responding in African American Vernacular English (AAVE)
- 🔐 Secure login/logout system
- 🖥️ Visual dashboard with trade summaries and live paper balance

---

## 🔐 Features

- Secure login with session memory
- Real-time trade simulation interface
- AAVE-style GPT-4 chat assistant for education & trade coaching
- Clean, professional UI styled like a Series B fintech dashboard
- Streamlit-based architecture for quick launches

---

